author: Kirthana Sasitharan
title: Ontario MPP returns to health-care front lines to assist COVID-19 pandemic response
description: Mississauga MPP Natalie Kusendova, is returning to her previous role as a registered nurse, to help alleviate the burden on her colleagues and assist with the fight against COVID-19.
content:
Natalie Kusendova is making the most of her time away from the Ontario Legislature, as it suspends the spring session temporarily amidst the COVID-19 pandemic. 
Instead, the Mississauga Centre MPP is going back to her roots as a registered nurse at Etobicoke… [+2520 chars]
